          <div class="leader-bio" id="mark-bio">With 20 years of experience as a software engineer, Mark brings his passion for clean code and automation to Hoogly, where he leads the platform's technical architecture. From fintech to education, he's built solutions that simplify complex problems, always with an eye on scalability and user experience. When he's not optimizing code, you'll find Mark on the badminton court or firing up the barbecue, making memories with his son.</div>
